quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  47,20,"Iwo amene amakhulupirira amati, “Kodi bwanji Mutu wina siudavumbulutsidwe?” Koma pamene mutu wotsimikiza uvumbulutsidwa ndipo kumenya nkhondo kulamulidwa mmenemo iwe udzaona iwo amene m’mitima mwawo muli matenda ali kukuyang’ana iwe ngati munthu amene ali kukomoka pamene imfa ili kudza kwa iye. Koma zinali bwino kwa iwo"
  47,21,"Kumvera ndi mau abwino (zikadakhala zinthu zabwino). Ndipo pamene nkhani iweruzidwa, ndipo iwo akadadzipereka mwachoonadi kwa Mulungu, ndithudi, zikadakhala zabwino kwa iwo"
  47,22,"Kodi ngati inu mukadapatsidwa udindo wolamulira, mukadachita zinthu zoipa padziko ndi kuphwanya ubale wanu ndi anthu a mtundu wanu"
  47,23,Amenewa ndiwo amene Mulungu wawatemberera ndipo Iye wawapanga iwo kukhala osamva ndi akhungu
  47,24,Kodi iwo sangaganize za uthenga wa m’Korani? Kodi kapena mitima yawo ndi yotsekedwa
  47,25,"Ndithudi iwo amene amabwerera m’mbuyo ndi kukhalanso osakhulupirira pamene atalandira kale ulangizi, amatsogozedwa ndi Satana amene amawanamiza ndi zinthu zopanda pake"
  47,26,"Ichi ndi chifukwa chakuti iwo amanena kwa iwo amene amadana ndi zimene Mulungu wavumbulutsa kuti, “Ife tidzakumverani mu zina za nkhani zimenezi.” Koma Mulungu amadziwa zinsinsi zawo zonse"
  47,27,Kodi iwo adzachita chiyani pamene angelo adzalanda miyoyo yawo ndi kuwamenya pa nkhope ndi m’misana yawo
  47,28,Ichi ndi chifukwa chakuti iwo amatsatira zinthu zimene zimakwiyitsa Mulungu ndipo amadana ndi zimene zimamukondweretsa Iye. Kotero Mulungu adasandutsa ntchito zawo kukhala zinthu zopanda pake
  47,29,Kodi iwo amene m’mitima mwawo muli matenda amaganiza kuti Mulungu sadzaulula zoipa zawo zonse